data.description: This spacious corner lot has endless potential. It is located at a dead end and has a large backyard, with a swimming pool above the ground situated in the corner. The bathrooms have been renovated in a modern style, and the house has three bedrooms, along with a bonus room, and two and a half bathrooms. There is also a small, active chicken farm on the property. All the appliances are brand new, as well as the air conditioning unit. The seller is highly motivated, flexible, and ready for a quick sale. This home is definitely worth checking out!
